                  Specifically, the FDA's guidance statement elaborates on =
current=20
                  regulations that state that any product, food, or supplem=
ent=20
                  making health claims must be carefully policed by the FDA=
. This=20
                  has been a longtime FDA rule. Notably, the document sugge=
sts=20
                  that foods such as vegetable juices making health claims =
must=20
                  undergo federal monitoring. Because this is a =
&quot;guida=
